            "ratingValue": "2",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I want to share my experience with this School. At first instance, you will find this school, a very large institute with good sports facilities. My meeting with the Previous Principal Mr.Puri was great. He is a true Gentleman, very supportive and visionary. Sports teachers are professional. The Chairman is very polite and humble.\nNow the main issue that stopped me from admitting my son to this school was their INTERNAL POLITICS  due to which the good staff left this school including the Principal Mr.Puri. Some of the staff ask us to come for admission and some of the senior staff were refusing, it seems that they all are not having any synergies. I got strong negative vibes about the environment of the school.\nI don't know what other people think about this school but this could be the reason that despite such a large facility the strength of the school is very less.",
